abia; Othman, M.N., (1983) Water and Development in Saudi Arabia, , Tuhamah Publication, Jeddah, Saudi Arabia; Pachauri, R.K., Damodaran, M., Wait and see versus no regrets: Comparing the costs of economic strategies (1992) Confronting Climatic Change: Risks, Implications, and Responses, , Mintzer, I. M. (ed.), Chapter 6, Cambridge University Press; Parry, M.L., (1990) Climate Change and World Agriculture, , Chapter 8, Earthscan Publication, London; Parry, M.L., Rosenzweig, C., Iglesias, A., Fischer, G., Livermore, M., Climate change and world food security: A new assessment (1999) Global Environ. Change, 9, pp. S51-S67; Parry, M.L., Swaminathan, M.S., Effect of climatic change on food production (1993) Confronting Climatic Change: Risks, Implications, and Responses, , Mintzer, I. M. (ed.), Chapter 8, Cambridge University Press; Rosenzweig, C., Tubiello, F.N., Impact of global climate change on Mediterranean agriculture: Current methodologies and future directions: An introductory essay (1997) Mitig. Adapt. Strat. Global Change, 1, pp. 219-232; Sagga, A.M., (1998) Physical Geography of Saudi Arabia, , Sagga, Dar Kunoz Press, Jeddah, Saudi Arabia; (1992) National Reports to the United Nations Conference on Environmental and Development (UNCED), , in Brazil; Schmandt, J., Clarkson, J., (1992) The Regions and Global Warming: Impacts and Response Strategies, , Oxford University Press; Schneider, S.H., (1993) Scenarios of Global Wanning, Biotic Interactions and Global Change, , Chapter 2, Sinauer Associates, Sunderland, Massachusetts; Sherffler, J.H., Heat island convergence in St. Louis during calm periods (1979) J. Appl. Meteorol., 18, pp. 1512-1520; Smith, B., Dennis, T., (1989) The Potential Effect of Global Climate Change, pp. 166-185. , A Report to the Congress of the U.S., EPA, December 1998; Vukovich, F.M., Williams, J.K., A theoretical study of the St. Louis heat island: Comparison between observed data and simulation results on the urban heat island circulation